{
  "id": "adv_group_mna_01_15",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 01 15",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-evening",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "……君、{user}君？\nお茶、もう下げてもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ {user}?\nDo you mind if I clear the tea?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……{user}君",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "元気だよ、元気！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're okay‚ right? You're okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと、外、出てきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'll step outside for a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.666666666667,
          "startTime": 13.533333333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4600,
          "startTime": 15.666666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに肩落として……三枝さん\n{user}君、大丈夫でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He looked so dejected… Saegusa-san.\nIs {user} okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あいつが一番麻奈と一緒に居たんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He was with Mana the most…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ショックは俺達とは比べ物にならないだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our shock doesn’t even compare with his.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "私達どうすれば……。このままだと\n事務所辞めちゃうかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should we do? At this rate‚\nhe might quit the company.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……そうかもしれない。あいつを立ち直らせることが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Maybe so. The only person who can",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "出来るのは、天国にいる麻奈だけなんだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "get him back on his feet is Mana‚ who is no longer here with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-03.m4a",
