      "text": "（この場所から、俺と麻奈の）\n（光と陰の交差が始まったんだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It was from here that）\n（the light and dark of Mana and I intersected…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}くん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こら。聞こえない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. Can’t you hear me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 96.76666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何、びっくりしてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so surprised?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ま……な……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ma… na?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……久しぶりね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s been a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺は夢でも見てるのか？　いや、夢でもいい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Am I dreaming? No‚ I don’t mind if it’s a dream…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 114.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 116.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺は……ずっと……\n会いたかったんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve…\nwanted to see you this whole time….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ごめんね。あの日、会場に行けなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry I couldn’t make it to the venue that day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 130.66666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あとこれ、夢じゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ this isn’t a dream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私、今、幽霊やってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m a ghost now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_15-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺が今までどんな気持ちで……え……幽霊？\n……おい、嘘だろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you have any idea what I’ve… Huh? A ghost?\n…You’re joking‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うーらーめーしーやー♪",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Boooooo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-night",
